ps: im really pissed now. having to add this map 6 times. sometimes the site crashed while uploading -.-. then 4 times it gives me an error by adding the map at the end. than its deleted because in one version, ive forgotten to fill in the subcategory. FPSbanana is a good site, but there have to be some bugfixes.
